Summary: ['Policy issued to Heartland Reformed Church.', 'Provides Commercial General Liability coverage from US Liability Insurance Company.', 'The policy period is December 31, 2024, to December 31, 2025.', 'The total premium for this coverage part is $504.00.', 'General aggregate liability limit is $2,000,000; each occurrence limit is $1,000,000.', 'Abuse and Molestation Liability coverage has a $300,000 aggregate limit.', 'Pastoral Professional Liability coverage has a $1,000,000 aggregate limit.', 'The insured is identified as a non-profit place of worship.']

['Auto insurance protects policyholders from financial loss due to vehicle accidents, theft, or damage.', 'Standard policies cover the named insured, spouse, resident relatives, and occasional permissive drivers.', 'Key coverages include liability, collision, comprehensive, medical, and uninsured motorist protection.', 'Premiums are calculated based on age, driving record, location, vehicle type, mileage, and credit score.', 'Various discounts reward safe drivers, multi-policy holders, good students, and anti-theft measures.', 'The claims process involves reporting, inspection, liability review, and settlement after an incident.']

['Semantic Kernel (SK) orchestrates LLMs, memory, plugins, and prompts for agentic applications.', 'Core SK components include AI service, vector store, and plugin connectors.', 'Plugins encapsulate functions from native code, OpenAPI, or prompt templates.', 'Prompt templates combine context, instructions, and function output for chat flows.', 'Filters provide hooks for pre/post event processing during the chat flow.', 'The kernel integrates these components to process user messages and return AI responses.', 'Plugins are crucial for exposing business logic and data sources efficiently.', 'SK is ideal for knowledge assistants, enterprise workflows, and tool-enabled agents.']
